WEBVTT

00:00:01.120 --> 00:00:09.399
All right. Well, just let me know when everybody's here. I'm just going to sing a little bit before everybody comes in.

00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:26.799
Only believe. Only believe. All things are possible. Only believe.

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:43.279
Only believe. Only believe. All things are possible when you only believe.

00:00:43.280 --> 00:01:05.238
Lord, I believe. Lord, I believe. All things are possible. Lord, I believe.

00:01:05.239 --> 00:01:25.319
Lord, I receive. Lord, I receive. All things are possible. Lord, I receive.

00:01:25.320 --> 00:01:30.639
Well, good morning family. Thank you for joining us again today.

00:01:30.640 --> 00:01:35.279
I'm going to just take the time right now and anoint myself with oil.

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:42.083
I believe with all my heart in anointing yourself with oil in these last days.

00:01:42.084 --> 00:01:49.277
You need to do it every single day. I anoint my kids. I anoint my wife. I anoint everything.

00:01:49.278 --> 00:01:57.759
I walk around with a bottle of oil in my pocket because I just believe in the power of the blood of Jesus.

00:01:57.760 --> 00:02:06.183
I don't want to make it a religious habit, but I do it because of the relationship of just honoring the blood of Jesus, honoring my covenant.

00:02:06.184 --> 00:02:11.367
That's why we take communion all the time. We got communion all over the place.

00:02:11.368 --> 00:02:28.345
And as I was watching some of the prayer breakfast this morning and seeing where we are as a nation and the valley of decision of where President Trump is, we're in that place right now that the Lord showed us.

00:02:28.346 --> 00:02:34.039
And I didn't realize the prayer breakfast was on the 4th, the day after the 3rd.

00:02:34.040 --> 00:02:40.945
He came in and he said a lot of things about making this nation one nation under God again.

00:02:40.946 --> 00:02:46.294
He wanted to do a big prayer thing, which Brayden can show you a clip.

00:02:46.295 --> 00:02:54.760
There's a prayer breakfast he wants to do like a prayer at the National Mall or whatever on the 17th of May.

00:02:54.761 --> 00:03:06.799
He wants to dedicate this nation back to God in prayer. And I think that's a great step. I believe we can work with that.

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:22.238
From what I have seen coming even today interceding for this nation, the Lord keeps talking about a humbling is coming, a shaking is coming to bring the bride back to his side.

00:03:22.239 --> 00:03:35.888
And in his speech yesterday, he even talked about the speaker of the house being real religious and he said, "I want to be around him more because I don't know if God would protect me like he would him.

00:03:35.889 --> 00:03:40.127
So, I want to hang around him more."You can see the clip there if you want to see it.

00:03:40.128 --> 00:03:46.359
But you know, Mike Johnson is a very religious person and he does not hide it.

00:03:46.360 --> 00:04:02.270
He'll say to me sometimes at lunch, "Sir, may we pray?"I say, "Excuse me, what happened at lunch?"It's okay with me, but he's a very religious person and he is popular and he's doing an unbelievable job.

00:04:02.271 --> 00:04:12.279
So, I think God is watching over him. I don't know about me, so I hang around with him because I feel I'm protected a little bit.

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:19.866
Sir, we believe that God is protecting you, too. We're praying for you.

00:04:19.867 --> 00:04:36.662
We're excited that you would be excited to have a day of prayer and that you would show up and pray that you would say, "Hey, we want to make this nation a nation under God again and declare it as the head of the nation."We pray for your protection.

00:04:36.663 --> 00:04:57.839
We pray for your wisdom in leading the nation, praying for you to be a God-fearing man, a backbone like a crowbar, that you're not full of pride, that you're humble before the Lord, and that God will use you in these last days.

00:04:57.840 --> 00:05:02.679
I'm excited about what you said today. I'm excited about some of the things.

00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:07.839
Yeah, I believe as the body of Christ, we need to work with this. We need to back you.

00:05:07.840 --> 00:05:16.594
Let's pray for him as we see crypto and these things tanking, gold and silver and all these things.

00:05:16.595 --> 00:05:39.742
I said, "Lord, I need that window."There's certain cryptos that fell really hard over the last couple of days and I thought, Lord, is this a great buying opportunity or is this what I saw about the great financial start?

00:05:39.743 --> 00:05:46.719
What I heard when I was praying today the Lord said, Braden, it's trying to come on early.

00:05:46.720 --> 00:05:52.910
It's trying to come on early, what you saw about the great financial shaking and things.

00:05:52.911 --> 00:06:02.479
It's trying to come on early. You must hold it back in prayer.

00:06:02.480 --> 00:06:10.919
If you don't contend for what I have for you, this is Satan's wheelhouse, the finances.

00:06:10.920 --> 00:06:22.248
And as the elite of what I told you, the Illuminati with the mask and all the things that I saw are being exposed and the darkness is being covered.

00:06:22.249 --> 00:06:28.799
They will do things in retaliation against the economy on purpose.

00:06:28.800 --> 00:06:47.799
They have the ability to do that by pulling their money out and doing things to try to manipulate the economy, to try to manipulate the dollar, to try to do what they got to do with the power that they have to leverage it with what the devil is telling them to do.

00:06:47.800 --> 00:06:58.697
And if they can try to sink the ship early, they will do so. So what do we do as the church?

00:06:58.698 --> 00:07:06.439
We pray. The devil knows the words and they know. He knows they're accurate. He knows what the Lord is saying.

00:07:06.440 --> 00:07:18.759
He knows what the Lord has planned for his body and I told you 1% of the people, if you're listening, will walk in the end time wealth transfer, 1%, because the others are not listening.

00:07:18.760 --> 00:07:31.199
They're not walking by his side. And so I see the things happening and people are upset and oh, it looks so bad. It looks like blood is in the streets.

00:07:31.200 --> 00:07:42.226
But instantaneously, instead of being moved by what I see or what I feel, I have to just go vertical and sit there and go, "Hey God, it's in your hands."I use my authority.

00:07:42.227 --> 00:08:00.294
We pray and we do everything we can but ultimately I was still singing the song. I know the sorrow and I know it all.

00:08:00.295 --> 00:08:08.205
I don't know all the words, because whenever I don't know all the words I make them up to him, but he knows what I'm saying.

00:08:08.206 --> 00:08:16.305
Braden, he knows I just sit there and sing to the Lord. It'll all go away if you just say the word.

00:08:16.306 --> 00:08:51.359
But even if you don't, you know that one by Mercy Me, that song, "It is well with my soul."Whenever you see all these things happening, it is well, it is well with my soul.

00:08:51.360 --> 00:09:10.008
I was singing that out in the shower today. And there's something when you realize that no matter how much I know that the word of faith, we believe we have power and life and death is in our tongue.

00:09:10.009 --> 00:09:18.719
That's what the Bible says. But there's a certain place that you've done all you can do, is stand and stand there.

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:22.799
And you don't always see the result of what you're believing for.

00:09:22.800 --> 00:09:33.679
Sometimes people go home early. Sometimes things happen. But that is where I said, it is well with my soul.

00:09:33.680 --> 00:09:56.199
Regardless of what I see and what I feel, if it don't always pan out the way you thought it would, I keep my eyes on Jesus and always maintain that place of praise and glory even whenever I don't always see what I wanted to see.

00:09:56.200 --> 00:10:06.236
Does that make sense what I'm saying to you? There were so many times even with Megan years and years I thought, "Lord, do you see what I'm going through?

00:10:06.237 --> 00:10:31.777
Do you feel my pain with my little girl and the things that we've walked through?"But yesterday, Diana was in and she said, "Braden, I felt the Lord say to take Megan to get her hair done."I said, and instantaneously I'm thinking, do you remember what happened last time we did that?

00:10:31.778 --> 00:10:38.092
Back when she was six years old. She's 21 now, next month. And she has never had her hair done.

00:10:38.093 --> 00:10:49.950
I always trim it to try to keep it out of her face so she doesn't get her she wads it up and gets in huge knots in her hair all the time because she's always touching it and doing things, you know.

00:10:49.951 --> 00:10:59.099
And I thought, well, I trust that you heard the Lord. But Megan doesn't like it when people put scissors next to her face.

00:10:59.100 --> 00:11:05.875
She doesn't like the people putting their hands next to her, you know, like most people don't.

00:11:05.876 --> 00:11:14.759
You know, you put your hand next to my eyes, I'm going to try to freak out and bite you or whatever, you know, but Megan has never been a person who likes that.

00:11:14.760 --> 00:11:36.209
And so last time we went to the barber, the salon or whatever, I had to hold her arms with the cape around both of us and had that person cutting her hair and Megan was trying to bite them the whole time they were trying to cut her hair.

00:11:36.210 --> 00:11:50.039
She was screaming at the top of her lungs to the point where we were so embarrassed after we left because the place was full that I vowed I'd never do that again to her.

00:11:50.040 --> 00:12:01.679
So when Diana said, "You know, Brandon, I heard the Lord today,"I said, "Baby, I trust you. Let's do it."So we called the people and we got right in.

00:12:01.680 --> 00:12:18.119
And as Megan sat there and they washed her hair and got all the knots out because we try so hard to keep her hair—but when you're dealing with somebody that is always doing that stuff, it's very interesting.

00:12:18.120 --> 00:12:30.613
Unless you live it, you never understand it. As we were going there and all that was happening yesterday, there was such a peace on Megan.

00:12:30.614 --> 00:12:35.519
She was enjoying it. She was giggling. She was laughing as the people were washing her hair.

00:12:35.520 --> 00:12:42.639
As she sat there, I sat over to the side this time because both of us couldn't fit in the chair.

00:12:42.640 --> 00:12:51.449
She sat there and the lady was brushing her hair and combing all the knots out and cleaning her hair up and was cutting and she did the whole hair.

00:12:51.450 --> 00:12:58.551
And Megan sat there looking at herself in the mirror this time, acting like everything was okay.

00:12:58.552 --> 00:13:11.799
Yeah, she still put her hands on her ears because the beauticians were loud or whatever, but she got her first style and haircut at 21 years old.

00:13:11.800 --> 00:13:28.039
It was something that we—as Diana was getting her hair next to her done in Paisley—all my girls got their hair done for the first time together as a family, a girls'day.

00:13:28.040 --> 00:13:42.575
As you pray and you say, "It is well with my soul."And you go through the sorrow and you don't know the hurt, it'll all go away if you just say the word.

00:13:42.576 --> 00:14:09.519
But even if you don't—but in that circumstance when you're believing and you get your breakthrough and you have your suddenly, you have your suddenly—the expiration date to the problem.

00:14:09.520 --> 00:14:29.719
Never forget where you come from. Now that you can see it happen, something that you always longed for, to have your daughter always look nice and to have her hair done right.

00:14:29.720 --> 00:14:43.395
Never forget where God brought you from. Never forget the valley.

00:14:43.396 --> 00:14:52.007
I still pinch myself when she's sitting there getting her teeth cleaned like when she got them done this last week.

00:14:52.008 --> 00:14:54.999
And the dentist looked at her at that time and he looked at her again.

00:14:55.000 --> 00:15:03.938
He goes, "My goodness, look how far your little girl's come."He's a Christian. He's a believer.

00:15:03.939 --> 00:15:12.559
And as Megan's getting her teeth X-rayed and doing all that, she didn't even do anything; she just let him clean them.

00:15:12.560 --> 00:15:38.119
But as I saw her sitting there getting her hair done and they were brushing it up and combing and doing all these things and blow-drying, they thought we were strange because of the way Diana and I both were watching with our mouths open because we were witnessing a miracle.

00:15:38.120 --> 00:15:51.519
A lot of people will never understand the miracle whenever they see the manifestation around you because they didn't walk in the valley.

00:15:51.520 --> 00:16:05.919
But when you see God show up after 21 years, you get a breakthrough.

00:16:05.920 --> 00:16:21.449
I cry because it's something that I've believed for for so long. And yesterday was one of those days you just get through...

00:16:21.450 --> 00:16:37.319
and the bombardment of the pressure from the world and the things that I've dealt with lately from this channel, praying for our president that I know that God has assigned me to pray for him.

00:16:37.320 --> 00:16:58.479
And I'm so thankful that there's so many of you that take this prayer channel seriously even whenever I have an off day like we did this last time and the Lord says, "I just want you to show by example."That I don't use the Lord, he uses me.

00:16:58.480 --> 00:17:09.510
I don't tap into it, he allows me to use it. I have this treasure in earthen vessels that the excellency of the power is known of him and not of me.

00:17:09.511 --> 00:17:16.198
No matter how much I see or what I don't see, we give all the glory to God.

00:17:16.199 --> 00:17:25.482
And I know you've heard me say that a thousand times, but you'll hear me say it a thousand more because you saw that it is not random Biggs.

00:17:25.483 --> 00:17:29.600
I believe some of you are just like whatever. I don't care what you think.

00:17:29.601 --> 00:17:52.953
But I was so taken these last two days to pray over things and pray over the valley of decision and where President Trump is with the nation and praying over Israel, praying over the finances of the nation because of how serious things are right now.

00:17:52.954 --> 00:18:08.799
If people didn't realize how much we're on rice paper right now, the escalation of things, the acceleration of things of the end times is all around us.

00:18:08.800 --> 00:18:19.492
And most people have their head in the sand. They're too busy typing in the chat, "How are you doing, sister clipboard?"And I'm just like, "Do you understand?

00:18:19.493 --> 00:18:34.023
It's a holy moment."The chat is toxic. There's so many people that lose themselves in just trying to entertain themselves.

00:18:34.024 --> 00:18:44.039
God is in the still small voice. He's in the moment that is not the shock and awe.

00:18:44.040 --> 00:18:52.279
He's not insecure. He doesn't need that to validate he is God. He is God regardless.

00:18:52.280 --> 00:19:02.592
And even with Diana saying, "Lord, are you upset about the AI?"They're going to try to discredit the miracles in the days ahead.

00:19:02.593 --> 00:19:17.439
People will question whether or not you really did it or not. And he said, "Good."Diana said, "What?"He said, "Good.

00:19:17.440 --> 00:19:34.986
Blessed are those that have not seen yet still believe."So you're not bothered by AI trying to discredit the miracles that are about to take place, people trying to question him if it's authentic or not.

00:19:34.987 --> 00:19:50.119
God's not insecure. God does not need to be validated. He's worthy and he deserves all the honor and all the praise of everything we ever do.

00:19:50.120 --> 00:20:04.879
But God's not looking for you to go, "Hey, I need to know. I need you, Brandon, to validate me to make me feel like I'm God today."He's secure in who he is.

00:20:04.880 --> 00:20:12.174
He doesn't need me to go, "You know what? The AI disproved you, Lord."I really think he's like, "I don't care about what...

00:20:12.175 --> 00:20:23.839
I'm God. I'm secure in who I am. I am that I am. Either you believe it or you don't. But I don't care if you do or if you don't.

00:20:23.840 --> 00:20:30.945
I don't need your validation, Brandon."So many times I think these prophetic channels need to be validated.

00:20:30.946 --> 00:20:48.140
I've seen and been insecure about it myself, needing them to see that I was right and what the Lord said to me because you want people to—it's like everybody says, "You need to be acid tested, Brandon.

00:20:48.141 --> 00:21:01.093
You need to be acid tested, your words that you give. You say so much, you need an acid test."So when I have an acid test moment, I try to show everybody because you need that validation from people to let you know, to say, "I heard it.

00:21:01.094 --> 00:21:15.359
I see. I told you I heard it."But when the Lord said... well, he said to Diana and me both after it was over because I questioned, I sat there looking, "I don't need your validation.

00:21:15.360 --> 00:21:28.227
I'm confident in who I am."And when Diana said that, I questioned, I went, "Wow, baby. Wow."God is secure in who he is.

00:21:28.228 --> 00:21:40.759
And when Diana said that, it was beautiful because I realize that there's so much to that statement that he said to her.

00:21:40.760 --> 00:21:46.239
There's so much to the conversations because Diana thinks on a different level.

00:21:46.240 --> 00:21:59.396
I think real country backwoods, but Diana is really intellectual and analytical and she thinks real deep and she has these conversations with the Lord that are really humdingers—is what I want to call them.

00:21:59.397 --> 00:22:11.319
They make you think a lot. And the things that he says to her are so much different than me because all our relationships are so personal.

00:22:11.320 --> 00:22:15.959
Even her relationship with the Lord is so unique, not cookie cutter.

00:22:15.960 --> 00:22:20.112
If you're trying to imitate somebody else, you're missing it.

00:22:20.113 --> 00:22:27.279
You're fearfully and wonderfully made by yourself. You do not need to be a Brandon.

00:22:27.280 --> 00:22:36.199
You do not need to be a Diana. You just need to be you. So many times I wanted to be like Billy Graham.

00:22:36.200 --> 00:22:41.479
Boy, if you could give an altar call like Billy Graham, you'd be doing something.

00:22:41.480 --> 00:22:49.679
Or someone else who was in healing ministry—I won't mention his name now, but I want to be like that.

00:22:49.680 --> 00:22:56.097
Touch, fire, all this stuff. But the more I get to know certain people, I go, "You know what?

00:22:56.098 --> 00:23:07.399
I just need to be me."They have issues, and I don't want their issues with their tissues; I just need to be me.

00:23:07.400 --> 00:23:17.130
I don't dishonor them, and I look at where they've been and what they've achieved for the Lord, but I am fearfully and wonderfully made myself.

00:23:17.131 --> 00:23:26.159
There are no cookie cutters. There's no parroting. Just be unique and be authentic.

00:23:26.160 --> 00:23:40.039
As I watched this girl cut Megan's hair yesterday, she was a heavy-set girl and she was so confident in her ability to cut hair.

00:23:40.040 --> 00:23:50.730
She didn't question if she was too heavy or whatever; she wasn't trying to mimic herself off of somebody else.

00:23:50.731 --> 00:23:57.483
She was just doing her job and was an artist at what she was doing.

00:23:57.484 --> 00:24:06.999
I realize there are many times I feel like I don't fit the mold of what I'm supposed to be behind this camera for you.

00:24:07.000 --> 00:24:19.495
I'm too heavy, I'm not smart enough; there are so many things that try to disqualify me until the Lord showed me, "Just be confident in who you are.

00:24:19.496 --> 00:24:24.519
I'm working with your weight issues. I'm doing these things for you, Brandon.

00:24:24.520 --> 00:24:29.919
But there's nobody else who can do what I've called you to do.

00:24:29.920 --> 00:24:43.959
Just be you."I've just had those "come to Jesus"moments these last couple of days.

00:24:43.960 --> 00:24:52.559
After the last video, I was so upset about how everything went, and the Lord said, "I did that on purpose.

00:24:52.560 --> 00:25:04.839
It's not about you and people validating you. It's about them finding me.

00:25:04.840 --> 00:25:13.185
If your channel goes away, where will they be? Will they find me in a deeper intimacy?

00:25:13.186 --> 00:25:24.674
I want you to teach them to come to me. They don't need you; they just need me and them."Does that make sense?

00:25:24.675 --> 00:25:32.478
They need to go vertical. They don't need a relationship with you; they need it with me.

00:25:32.479 --> 00:25:34.683
Go vertical. And the things He says challenge me, and I sit there and go...

00:25:34.684 --> 00:25:47.999
He says, "If people look too much at man, I'll show that they're just man.

00:25:48.000 --> 00:26:00.199
I'll allow them to see how human you really are."So, I'm so thankful that you were able to see it.

00:26:00.200 --> 00:26:10.839
I fear Him. I fear Him as I hear so much toxicity in ministry nowadays.

00:26:10.840 --> 00:26:17.999
One minister said, "I won't preach anywhere unless I get $50,000 per time I speak.

00:26:18.000 --> 00:26:24.999
They have to raise that money before I'll even go there."I'm not mentioning his name.

00:26:25.000 --> 00:26:33.759
I saw the materialism of the church even more so lately—the big business side.

00:26:33.760 --> 00:26:46.879
And there is a side of this that is very scary to me. I refuse to be any part of it.

00:26:46.880 --> 00:27:13.470
I told the Lord, "What is it to gain the whole world and lose his soul?"I've seen that lately with offers and things you get, and you realize, "None of this will change me."None of this will change Diana; none of this will change him.

00:27:13.471 --> 00:27:20.561
But as He said, "Go back to the main thing all the time. Go back to the janitor.

00:27:20.562 --> 00:27:29.312
Go back to the way it was here. What got you here in the first place? Don't add to and supplement new things in.

00:27:29.313 --> 00:27:49.793
Just keep being alone with me."The guy that sits at the dryer and folds laundry, the one that cleans the toilets, the one that takes care of his kids—always keep the main thing the main thing, no matter how big things get around you.

00:27:49.794 --> 00:28:04.959
I realize it's not just an outward thing; it's a heart thing. There's a lot I see that's been bothering me lately.

00:28:04.960 --> 00:28:12.519
I've been very annoyed with people coming from Chicago and people coming to church. I go to church to go to church.

00:28:12.520 --> 00:28:22.689
I'm not there to answer your questions about what you should do to dig in the side of a mountain to find gold, or prophetic words where you're seeking a fortune teller.

00:28:22.690 --> 00:28:34.559
I'm not a fortune teller. I don't have control over it. But there are so many people—I've looked at the emails and the bombardment of things—you've lost your way.

00:28:34.560 --> 00:28:41.333
And I am not here to help you find it in that way. "What do I do with my life?"That's for God to tell you.

00:28:41.334 --> 00:28:50.079
I have no idea. But there are so many people that are so dysfunctional.

00:28:50.080 --> 00:28:58.399
There's so much dysfunction in the body of Christ. And I'm here to tell you: keep the main thing the main thing.

00:28:58.400 --> 00:29:09.550
Your dysfunction is a lack of vertical focus. You must keep your eyes on Him.

00:29:09.551 --> 00:29:17.799
Stop going horizontal. Horizontal is looking at me; horizontal is looking at your pastor.

00:29:17.800 --> 00:29:24.399
Keep your eyes on Jesus; He's the author and the finisher of our faith.

00:29:24.400 --> 00:29:31.679
If you keep your eyes on Him, everything else will line up perfectly. Do you understand?

00:29:31.680 --> 00:29:41.355
And there are so many of you thinking you're listening to the Lord, but you're listening to familiar spirits because you don't get in this book.

00:29:41.356 --> 00:29:47.853
You're looking through religious, weird eyes, and the things you're meditating on are demonic.

00:29:47.854 --> 00:29:51.375
You're listening to familiar spirits. I can see them behind your eyes when I'm there.

00:29:51.376 --> 00:29:55.039
But am I supposed to call you out and lay hands on you, cast the devils out of you right there?

00:29:55.040 --> 00:30:03.959
So you've got demons? No, because you're going to fight me. You want the devils you have, but I'm not here to pick at you.

00:30:03.960 --> 00:30:13.999
But I'm not going to allow you to waste my time. My time's precious to me.

00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:19.479
And there's so much of it lately—people trying to waste your time.

00:30:19.480 --> 00:30:26.273
Time wasters. Everybody feels they have an entitlement to talk to you.

00:30:26.274 --> 00:30:37.885
Everybody feels they have an entitlement to say something or whatever, and you go, "You don't have anything for me."I just go back to the little place of my square with my wife and my kids.

00:30:37.886 --> 00:30:44.683
And it's like Diana said to me: "Isn't it amazing how many people come out of the woodwork after all this?

00:30:44.684 --> 00:30:53.119
